text: When the Lord thy God shall have brought thee into the land, which thou art going into possess, and shall have destroyed many nations before thee, the Hethite, and the Gergesit, and the Amorite, and the Channonite, and the Pharasite, and the Heavot, and the Jebusit, many nations much more numerous than thou art, and stronger than thou.
